      "headline": "Healing the Leper",
      "verses": [
        {
          "verse": 1,
          "text": "When Jesus came down from the mountain, large crowds followed him."
        },
        {
          "verse": 2,
          "text": "And behold, a leper approached and knelt before him, saying, “Lord, if you will, you can make me clean.”"
        },
        {
          "verse": 3,
          "text": "Jesus stretched out his hand, touched him, and said, “I will; be cleansed.” and at once his leprosy was cleansed."
        },
        {
          "verse": 4,
          "text": "Then Jesus said to him, “See that you tell no one, but go show yourself to the priest and offer the gift Moses commanded, for a testimony to them.”"
        }
      ]
    },
