          "text": "“For I also am a man under authority, with soldiers under me. I say to one, ‘Go!’ and he goes; to another, ‘Come!’ and he comes; to my slave, ‘Do this!’ and he does it.”"
        },
        {
          "verse": 10,
          "text": "Jesus was amazed and said to those who were following him, “Amen I tell you, I have found such great faith with no one in Israel."
        },
        {
          "verse": 11,
          "text": "I tell you, many will come from east and west and be feasting with Abraham, Isaac, and Jacob in the kingdom of heaven."
        },
        {
          "verse": 12,
          "text": "But the sons of the kingdom will be cast out into the outer darkness, where there is weeping and gnashing of teeth.”"
        },
        {
          "verse": 13,
          "text": "Then Jesus said to the centurion, “Go; as you believed, let it be done to you.” And the slave was healed that very hour."
        }
      ]
